For developers, who are building real-time data-driven applications, Redis is the preferred, fastest, and most feature-rich cache, data structure server, and document and vector query engine.

Gin is a high-performance HTTP web framework written in Go. It provides a Martini-like API but with significantly better performanceup to 40 times fasterthanks to httprouter. Gin is designed for building REST APIs, web applications, and microservices.
